## **Notes**

### Networking

- Make 3 new connections a week, have 2 coffee chats
- Read "How to Win Friends and Influence People"
- Normal Follow-Up Schedule
  - Day 1 - Meet person (learn something unique or a passion they have)
  - Day 2 - Email them thank you and provide value for their passion
  - Day 4 - LinkedIn add and message, remind how you meet and thanks again I want to stay in touch hope to see you at the next meetup
  - Day 6 - Twitter
- Coffee Chat Schedule
  - Week 1 - Follow up email (You are where I'd like to be in a few years, would you be open to 15min chat about to learn a little bit about how you got there and your experiences?)
  - Week 2 - Follow up email
  - Week 4 - Last email
- Google Alerts (https://www.google.com/alerts#)
  - Create alerts for people and topics, when something new contact themGrant

